m6fa x7e h1f y780 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A delightful experience </div><div class="t m17b x7e h1f y781 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sacredness desecrated </div><div class="t m55 x7e h1f y682 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Subject of religious </div><div class="t m3e5 x1 h1f y782 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disputes </div><div class="t m3df x7e h1f y783 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Influenced by </div><div class="t m4ed x1 h1f y784 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pagan practices </div><div class="t m6fb x1 h1f y785 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and philosophies </div><div class="t m508 x2a h1f y786 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath </div><div class="t m2f8 x11 h20 y67e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gen. 2:3 </div><div class="t m27c x2a h20 y77f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ex. 20:8-11 </div><div class="t m6f xc4 h20 y780 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Isa. 58:13, 14 </div><div class="t m29b xc4 h20 y781 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Eze. 22:8 </div><div class="t m50 xc4 h20 y787 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mark 2:23, 24 </div><div class="t m6fc x11 h20 y783 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Observance </div><div class="t m6fd xc0 h20 y784 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">changed to </div><div class="t m564 x6d h20 y785 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accommodate </div><div class="t m6fe xc0 h20 y788 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">worshipers </div><div class="t m2fc xbc h1f y789 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Marriage </div><div class="t m6ff x7a h20 y78a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Gen. 5:2 </div><div class="t m147 x7a h20 y77f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Isa. 54:5, 6 </div><div class="t m700 x7a h20 y780 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prov. 5:18, 19 </div><div class="t m14d x7a h20 y78b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Eze. 22:9-11 </div><div class="t m427 x7a h20 y787 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mark 10:1-16 </div><div class="t m701 x7a h20 y78c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Conditioned by </div><div class="t m702 xb2 h20 y784 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Greek idea that </div><div class="t m703 xb2 h20 y785 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">body is inferior </div><div class="t m37c xb2 h20 y788 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to soul. </div><div class="t m704 x36 h1f y78d ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s ideal distorted. </div><div class="t m705 x67 h20 y78d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Desecration of the Sabbath parallels </div><div class="t m67f x7e h20 y78e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the desecration of marriage. Revival of true Sabbathkeeping </div><div class="t m395 x7e h20 y78f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will be accompanied by revival of Christian marriage. </div><div class="t m706 x36 h1f y790 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Devaluation of women. </div><div class="t m707 x6e h20 y790 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In pagan cultures, and even among </div><div class="t m708 x7e h20 y791 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the people of God, women were often regarded as property. </div><div class="t m691 x7e h20 y792 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Easy divorce for men, polygamy, and treatment of women as </div><div class="t m4af x7e h20 y793 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">inferiors corrupted God&apos;s plan. </div><div class="t m1c2 x36 h1f y794 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Violations of the marriage covenant: </div><div class="t m709 x76 h20 y794 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">adultery (2 Sam. 11:2, </div><div class="t m27 x7e h20 y795 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4), incest (Eze. 22:9-11), rape (2 Sam. 13:14), bestiality (Lev. </div><div class="t m70a x1d h20 y62 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">18:23), homosexuality (Rom. 1:26, 27), prostitution (Judges 16:1), </div><div class="t mbe x7e h20 y1b5 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">polygamy (2 Sam. 5:13), divorce, violence, and abuse (Mal. 2:16; </div><div class="t m70b x7e h20 y796 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Matt. 19:8). </div><div class="t m70c x36 h1f y797 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sexual renunciation or permissiveness. </div><div class="t m70d x9e h20 y798 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Throughout the </div><div class="t m70e x7e h20 y799 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Middle Ages celibacy and virginity were thought more holy </div><div class="t m613 x7e h20 y79a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">than marriage. This view is still held, though it is contrary to </div><div class="t m15c x1d h20 y79b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Scripture. (See Heb. 13:4.) By contrast, today sexual pleasure is </div><div class="t m70f x7e h20 y79c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">often divorced from true love within marriage. </div><div class="t m2d0 x7e h1f y1b6 ff1 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">64 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
